.IX Item "REAL*8, OPTIONAL"
\&\s-1WEIGHT_OPT\s0(\s-1KMAX\s0, \s-1KMAX\s0), \s-1UNWEIGHTED_COVAR\s0(\s-1KMAX\s0,\ \s-1KMAX\s0)
